TY  - JOUR
T1  - Shareholders as Creditors of First Resort
AU  - Bodnaruk, Andriy
AU  - Rossi, Marco
Y1  - 2020/06/10
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2019.3556
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2019.3556
T2  - Management Science
