T1  - Incremental vs. Breakthrough Innovation: The Role of Technology Spillovers
AU  - Byun, Seong K.
AU  - Oh, Jong-Min
AU  - Xia, Han
Y1  - 2020/05/20
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2019.3507
